<br>
<br>
-immediate 20% increase to DD and rain damage<br>
<br>
We're supposed to be the masters in this category, and I believe we should be so decisively. A few points difference in mana cost or damage output and a second or two difference in cast time does not a master make, heh. I'd honestly want to see more than 20%, but that would be a good start.<br>
<br>
-The Eye of Zomm line<br>
<br>
I know most folks don't really care about this sort of thing, but one of our monikers is Masters of Knowledge. The Eye of Zomm, since the &quot;nerf&quot;(heh) it's been scribed near the front of my spellbook. It's immensely useful for scouting around corners, taking screenshots, giving the layout, mobs and such for a given area to the group without risking a monk or anyone else who can agro and get squashed. I'd love to see further upgrades to it...upgrades with longer durations, faster speed, lev, better swimming skill, and so on. Not nearly as important as our other issues, but it'd be nice.<br>
<br>
-Wizard only Gear<br>
<br>
Not nearly enough class specific &quot;armor&quot; for wizards of real value. All the int classes get shafted in this manner...we all compete with each other fiercely for item drops with good mana and int...and often wind up rolling against rangers/SKs/pallies/monks because the item in question is all/all and has sta/str/dex/low weight(whatever). There needs to be more wizard only gear in the same vein as ranger only bows and SK/Pally only weapons. The only real weapon we have is our spellcraft and the only way to increase our power beyond simple levelling is gear that increases our manapool.<br>
<br>
<br>
Just my personal opinions, for what they're worth.<br>
- <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umaevenniia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maevenniia</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/15/02 2:54:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=659.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: some other thoughts</span><hr size=1> <br>
