<br>
How about a /TGT command?  /tagetgrouptranslocate, like /tgb, it would allow a wizard to translocate people/groups they aren't a member of, allowing the porter to remain in his/her current group and not disrupt things.  It would have to be Translocate spells since those have a consent box anyways, preventing mischievous porters from sending people off to exotic locales without their consent <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
