<br>
perhaps the damage formula, costs, etc needs tweaking, I'm no expert at this..but I think from a roleplay perspective, I would picture a wizard so focused on outputting damage that they do not realize the toll in energy and vitality it is taking on them....or they deliberately exclude this from their perception, sacrificing themselves for the good of the group....<br>
